  <bioghist id="aspace_a4b0bcded474aa990e3d1efdc2628ffa">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>H. Roy Kelley, an architect, attended Cornell University 1913-1915.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_c09b671a3643712b9dcd8aec5cba85d4">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Thirteen scrapbooks of designs, articles, and photographs of residences designed by Kelley. Also, postcard-size architectural drawings done as a student at Cornell under Professor Phelps.</p>  </scopecontent>
